X
p=\pi r^2=\pi/4
E[X]=kp=\frac{k\pi}{4},\  \ Var(X)=E[X^2]-E^2[X]=\frac{k\pi(4-\pi)}{16}
\hat\pi=4X/k
E[\hat\pi]=\pi, \  \ Var(\hat\pi)=\frac{\pi(4-\pi)}{k}
